dct_title_s: Geologic map of the Lopez Mountain quadrangle, San Luis Obispo County, California
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.
"Topographic base map from newest available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangle LOPEZ MOUNTAIN, CA 1965, DMA 1854 I SE -- Series V895, REVISED 1993, PHOTOINSPECTED 1978."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
